I have another out-of-left-field suggestion. If you like narrative shenanigans, watch Last Year at Marienbad. It is french, surrealist, and 'meta' in a surprisingly modern way. If you dig that, check out Cocteau's Orphee, a 50s surrealist retelling of the Myth of Orpheus.
